task.summary: Server now serves client website and statics
Server now allows localhost:3000 to be served the api
Changed api shoppingcart url and added price
Tested to add some css classes. Also added link to shoppingcart.
Now possible to search for shoppingcart either using full url or just id
Moved functions into class and added clone button with no feedback yet.
Now possible to show and hide modal
Now possible to move between items in modal. Ctrl+c also does this
Added keyboard input support for moving left and right in modal. Also escape for closing the modal.
Ctrl+C will now auto select next id
Added some kind of search for printers on client
Added a better search by using elasticlunr
Search result link now opens in new tab
Started to implement a CartAnalyzer. However babel has to be configured for server for this to work.
Npm start now works with server and auto refresh. CartAnalyzer.js also reads products from cart
Added tags for detecting different types of products
CartAnalyzer can now identify different types of products
Added a method to filter different types of parts
Added enviroment variables that gets added on runtime and build
Created a PrinterFactory and added environment variable for cors
